<div style="font-family:serif;">
:<font size="15">גּלגּלת</font></div>

===Pronunciation===
גּלגּלת / gûlgôleth / gul-go'-leth

===Etymology===
By reduplication from [[גּלל]] {{HH|1556}}; 

===Noun===
'''גּלגּלת'''

# A skull (as round); by implication a head (in enumeration of persons): - head, every man, poll, skull.

